<div id="review_2550917957" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2550917957" />
    <a title="Elizabeth Dragina" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/75350434-elizabeth-dragina"><img alt="Elizabeth Dragina" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623610502p2/75350434.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2550917957?book_show_action=true">Oct 06, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elizabeth Dragina" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elizabeth Dragina" href="/user/show/75350434-elizabeth-dragina">Elizabeth Dragina</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/75350434-elizabeth-dragina?shelf=memorable">memorable</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2550917957" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10525710346460330723">Ack!!! Such an amazing book!! I would give a review but I don&apos;t have a lot of time so I will say.... basically it&apos;s amazing and everyone who loves action, fighting, and growing characters needs to read this!!<br/><br/>I also will hate the covers as much as the next person because they could be so much better.</span>
  <span id="freeText10525710346460330723" style="display:none">Ack!!! Such an amazing book!! I would give a review but I don't have a lot of time so I will say.... basically it's amazing and everyone who loves action, fighting, and growing characters needs to read this!!<br /><br />I also will hate the covers as much as the next person because they could be so much better.</span>
